  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Role: Infant Educator</strong></li><li><strong>AOP Childcare Centre</strong></li><li><strong>5 day | 7am - 7pm Rotate shift is a MUST</strong></li><li><strong>Entitled to  AWS + Performance Bonus </strong></li><li><strong>Work location:  Punggol / Bartley / Tampines </strong></li></ul><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Obtained at least a Certificate in Infant Care (CIT), Advanced Certificate in Early Years (ACEY), Higher Certificate in Infant Care (HCIC), or its equivalent</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Role & Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Plan and carry out the daily programme, developmental and care-giving tasks as assigned</p></li><li><p>Attend to the health, hygiene and safety needs of the infants</p></li><li><p>Create a safe environment and provide the best possible care to infants under their care</p></li><li><p>Build and maintain good rapport with parents<br /></p><p><br /><strong>📲 Interested candidates, please WhatsApp your resume to: +65 9642 0989 (Han)</strong><br /><strong>📧 Or email your resume to: </strong><a href=\"https://employer.mycareersfuture.gov.sg/jobs/6723-sales-support-customer-care-executive-sgd-2600%E2%80%934000-industrial-services-north-area-post-sales-support-supreme-hr-advisory-a212f1138e3ddd0ad8ec472e0fc6a5d6/view#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">supreme.cc.han@gmail.com</a><strong></strong></p><p><strong>👤 Chaw Chiaw Han | R22106723 🏢 The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</strong></p><p></p></li></ul>",
